  type="article"
  publishedAt="2026-04-29"
  faqData={[{"question":"Are Costco hot dogs gluten free?","answer":"The hot dog meat itself does not contain gluten ingredients, but it is served in a wheat bun. Cross-contamination in the food court is likely."},{"question":"Is the bun safe for celiac patients?","answer":"No, the standard Costco hot dog bun contains wheat flour. People with celiac disease should avoid it unless they bring their own gluten-free bun."}]}
>
